Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.89,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:12.61,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,From the 9th grade, class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:15.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anyone named that in class 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:18.04,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It happened 26 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.29,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,She'd been popular ever since the 7th grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.71,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,She was smart, pretty, \Nand had a great personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:29.66,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,so she was loved by \Nstudents and teachers alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:33.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's at least one person \Nlike that in every grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:35.59,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,But shortly after she started the 9th grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.63,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:38.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:39.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.26,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:44.90,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,So, everyone was really shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:47.56,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Until, suddenly, someone said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:49.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Said what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.82,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,He pointed to Misaki's desk and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.57,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,"Misaki's right there. She's not dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:58.85,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.77,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was just an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:05.12,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,But from that day on, \Nclass 3 continued to behave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:07.02,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,as though Misaki was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:10.01,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:14.01,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,They kept up the act right up to graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.01,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Do Not Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:16.50,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,The principal even arranged to have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.46,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki's seat included in \Ntheir graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.17,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:22.53,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, if it ended there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.90,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:29.05,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of the story is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.07,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel? Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:22.99,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:28.29,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness, what a way to start your life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.70,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,You poor dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.78,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:37.35,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Don't you worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.74,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:41.02,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, does my dad know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.74,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.87,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,Yousuke is in India at the moment, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.47,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to tell him? I have his number.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:53.51,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you. I'll contact him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.24,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's probably best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:04:01.30,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,That Yousuke, he's such a dutiful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.97,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,In all this time since Ritsuko died...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:09.79,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Yomiyama River flowing \Nthrough the center of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.55,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,And can you see the grounds beyond it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.40,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.38,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.25,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.90,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's the school you'll be attending.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:25.10,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the same school you went to, Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.90,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, although that was 14 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,So my mother went there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:30.66,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.47,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,My sister Ritsuko also went to Yomi North.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:34.58,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yomi North?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.02,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yomiyama North Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:37.84,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:41.17,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Public schools are a little \Ndifferent from private schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.04,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,but it just takes some getting used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.59,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll get used to it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.04,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.60,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.29,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.31,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you prepare for life at Yomi North.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:05:00.32,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're reading King this \Ntime, mister horror lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.57,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll leave you guys alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:16.72,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,We're students of Yomiyama North \NJunior High's 9th grade, class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:18.60,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.98,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kazami. Tomohiko Kazami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.91,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sakuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.51,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nice to meet you. I'm Yukari Sakuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:28.61,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,And this is—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.98,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi Akazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.92,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.66,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi and I are class officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.87,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Akazawa is in charge of countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:45.02,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,We came here today as \Nrepresentatives of class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.45,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Countermeasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.21,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You just transferred here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:51.35,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that you were supposed to start
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.55,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,coming to school on Monday, \Nbut then suddenly got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:59.38,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,So we decided to visit you \Non behalf of the entire class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.19,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Um, here. These are from all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.30,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You moved here from Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:07.34,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:10.30,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,And you went to a private school there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.79,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.35,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,For family reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:19.23,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time living in Yomiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:20.97,Default,Kouchi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:25.31,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I thought maybe you used to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.51,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.86,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.49,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you stay for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.27,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.62,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.45,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was really young, so... maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:42.96,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:46.67,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,I made you a copy of all notes from \Nthe start of the first term.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.36,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.93,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll start going to school in early May,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:52.93,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll see you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:58.19,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.21,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:01.58,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.90,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.73,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Your first name's Kouichi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.82,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,May we call you Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.65,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.49,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We look forward to getting \Nto know you, Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.83,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Same here. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:33.18,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kouichi, are you sure you've \Nnever lived in Yomiyama before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:38.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.94,Default,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.23,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.07,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a Yomi North student?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.45,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something to do \Non the second basement level?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:43.66,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.63,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But the second basement level is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.38,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.22,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,My poor other half...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.47,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,...is waiting for me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.21,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.54,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:40.89,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:42.86,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:54.94,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mechanical Room - Boiler Room \N Morgue
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:15.34,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.34,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.80,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.07,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:24.68,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.69,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, good morning! \NHow're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.46,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.28,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's 2 A.M. over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:36.27,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,India sure is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.29,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.20,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to leave for school, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.32,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,This is your go-get-'em call. \NBe grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.76,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.84,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.78,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,How've things been since \Nyou got out of the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.82,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Kouichi? I wanted to say—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:51.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, the signal here is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.03,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:57.86,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:00.57,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a collapsed lung's not \Nthe end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.95,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,I had one, when I was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.93,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.63,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,I never told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.40,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want anyone telling \Nyou it's hereditary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.44,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.44,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,I actually had it twice, \Nbut never again after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.64,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,So if it's hereditary, you're all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.18,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:21.63,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as something that's in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.38,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,and go enjoy your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.36,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stress over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:29.21,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's my boy! Say hello to \Nyour grandparents for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.37,Default,Yousuke,0000,0000,0000,,Man, India is seriously hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:41.30,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Rei! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.86,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Rei is {\i1}your{\i0} name, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:46.49,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer! Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.51,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:56.65,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Moving along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:59.36,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,The third thing you need to know to \Nprepare yourself for Yomi North is:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.66,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Always uphold the class rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.59,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:07.02,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Things might be different in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:10.04,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,but here the group matters \Nmore than the individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.59,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:16.96,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the fourth thing you need to know is—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.05,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,Kouichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.42,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.72,Default,Ryouhei,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast, she says, Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:27.96,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.28,Default,Ryouhei,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:33.20,Default,Ryouhei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going back to the hospital today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.69,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've been discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.81,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I start school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:39.40,Default,Ryouhei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.73,Default,Ryouhei,0000,0000,0000,,You're already in junior high, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:44.66,Default,Ryouhei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.97,Default,Ryouhei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're feeling up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the 9th grade now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.08,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in high school next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:56.19,Default,Ryouhei,0000,0000,0000,,If only that hadn't happened to Ritsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:59.15,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,Kouichi, breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.38,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:02.84,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Rei? {\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:08.27,Default,Kubo,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll be able to get along with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:11.64,Default,Kubo,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any troubles at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.74,Default,Kubo,0000,0000,0000,,please don't hesitate to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:18.99,Default,Kubo,0000,0000,0000,,You can also talk to Ms. Mikami, \Nthe assistant homeroom teacher, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.23,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.65,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,We look forward to having you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.40,Default,Board,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}May 6 (Wed.)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:36.17,Default,Board,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kouichi Sakakibara
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:36.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I moved here because of my father's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:39.09,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm living with my grandparents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.54,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,And, um, it's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:49.97,Default,Kubo,0000,0000,0000,,Please give our new friend \Na warm welcome, class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:53.68,Default,Kubo,0000,0000,0000,,Help each other, and work \Nyour hardest together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:59.69,Default,Kubo,0000,0000,0000,,so that you can all graduate \Nin prime health next March.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:04.04,Default,Kubo,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara, you can take that seat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.15,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.75,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all healed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.00,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.13,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,How does this town compare to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:32.51,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.19,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,But Tokyo sounds so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.95,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Small country towns like Yomiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.94,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,have nothing going for them these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.21,Default,Teshy,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.94,Default,Teshy,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing interesting happens here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.32,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo has its downsides, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.69,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so noisy, you can't relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.57,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it might seem that \Nway, if you've lived there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.95,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.95,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to try living in Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:56.24,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I like it better here. It's much quieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:57.58,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,And you're surrounded by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:00.71,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,That's an opinion you'd only hear \Nfrom someone who lived in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:03.53,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,I heard your dad is a college professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:05.96,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,And he's researching \Nin a foreign country now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.72,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.39,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.34,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kubodera told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.60,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he did? And about my old school, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.02,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much everyone knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.23,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Mikami talked to us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.43,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:23.13,Default,Teshy,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad Ms. Mikami \Nisn't our homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.48,Default,Teshy,0000,0000,0000,,She's hot, and she's got killer style, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.52,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:31.86,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Pretty women not your type, Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.10,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:36.43,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Then what kind of girl \Ndo you like, Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.46,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:40.32,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what country is your dad in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:41.08,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,India.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.21,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,He's been there about a year this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.78,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, India, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.77,Default,Teshy,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's hot there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.16,Default,Teshy,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to take it. I can't stand heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.58,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,Consider yourself lucky, Teshy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.02,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you try,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.90,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,you're never gonna do research \Nin a place like India.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.07,Default,Teshy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I'm well aware!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:03.81,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.56,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.41,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wondering about the \Nother girl who visited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.28,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Akazawa, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.49,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is she absent today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.91,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:19.30,Default,Teshy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why don't we give you a \Ntour of the school during lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:20.70,Default,Teshy,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough not knowing where stuff is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.33,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.67,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:25.56,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.58,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.12,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you want to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.36,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I love running.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.52,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:52.36,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,So, you've run before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.03,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:58.91,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you have a heart condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.51,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was born with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.97,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't know what it feels like to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.13,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could run with all my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.88,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You might be able to someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.26,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe you're right. Someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.42,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:31.50,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,...go to the nurse's office to lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:32.24,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.64,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.38,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,I can get there by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.08,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.37,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Takabayashi go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.88,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,To rest in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.46,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:57.65,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I fell yesterday and sprained my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:02.36,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,So, we don't share P.E. \Nwith another class here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:05.24,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Only class 3 is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:09.36,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Classes 1 and 2, and classes \N4 and 5, have P.E. together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.49,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You walked around with Kazami, Teshigawara,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.05,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,and the others during lunch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:16.69,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:20.34,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Did they say anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.25,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,They just gave me a tour of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:23.26,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:23.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:27.83,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.59,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,If we're not careful, \NAkazawa will yell at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sakuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.84,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.65,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:42.22,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.42,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.51,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The girl named Mei Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:50.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The one wearing an eyepatch on her left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:53.65,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see her in the classroom at lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:10.00,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.33,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.36,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You watching the P.E. class, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:40.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Should you be up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:42.46,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.89,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no point in \Nwatching from up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.62,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,And you? Should you be up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:54.13,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Were you drawing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.47,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,How do you write "Mei"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.01,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,With the character that means "sing."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.81,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The same character used \Nin "sympathy" and "scream."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:13.94,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:18.80,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you remember meeting me \Nat Yomiyama Hospital the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.27,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,In the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You got off at the second basement level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:29.58,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Did something like that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.94,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What did you go to the \Nsecond basement level for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.65,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You said you had something to deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.12,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You were holding some kind of white doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:36.97,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you had to deliver—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:39.38,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I hate being questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.82,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:43.09,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to force you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:45.13,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I just, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:51.02,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Something very sad happened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:58.92,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You are Kouichi Sakakibara, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:20:59.81,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:01.86,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Your classmates haven't told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.28,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Told me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:08.15,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,They associate your name with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:10.98,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But not just any death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:16.54,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,A cruel, irrational death that \Ntook place at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:21.81,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,This school is in a place close to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:24.05,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,especially the 9th grade's class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:28.68,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It's much, much closer to it \Nthan any of the other classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.56,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,To... death?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:36.19,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know anything, Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.90,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.53,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody has told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.02,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.90,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:50.35,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't try to get close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:54.79,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't talk to me anymore, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:56.56,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.93,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.96,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:09.70,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:13.31,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-ka-ki-ba-ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:48.50,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting along with your classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:51.23,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:00.28,Default,Tamie,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:02.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.86,0:24:50.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Blueprint.
